def binary_search(values, target):
    lo, hi = 0, len(values) - 1
    while lo <= hi:
        mid = (lo + hi) // 2
        if values[mid] == target:
            return mid
        if values[mid] < target:
            lo = mid + 1
        else:
            hi = mid - 1
    return -1
```
This assumes `values` is sorted in ascending order and runs in `O(log n)` time.

